HEADWORD: Ootype
<hw>O"o*type</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ +
<ets>-type</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The part of the oviduct
